{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "f1a2b3c4-d5e6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
    "name": "Flash Sale Engine - Complete API Test Suite",
    "description": "Comprehensive Postman Collection covering all REST endpoints of the Flash Sale Engine.\n\nRun requests in order (01 → 17):\n1. Auth: register → login → /me\n2. Products: create → get by UUID → list all\n3. Sale Admin: create sale → add item → activate\n4. Purchase & Orders: purchase item → get order\n5. Token: refresh → logout\n6. Rate limit & Redis pipeline tests\n\nAll tokens and UUIDs are automatically captured into collection variables.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "01 - Register Admin User",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Register: 200 OK or 400 already exists', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([200, 400]);",
                  "});",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.test('Response has email', function () { pm.expect(j).to.have.property('email'); });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"postman_admin@flashsale.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"role\": \"ADMIN\",\n  \"fullName\": \"Postman Admin User\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "register"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
